    "description": "《幻想战略录》是一款即时战略游戏<br>玩家需要选择喜欢的势力，收集散布在地图上的资源，<br>最终打倒所有其他对手，获得胜利。<br><br>运筹帷幄、决胜千里，樯橹灰飞烟灭！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超过40名东方Project人气角色闪亮登场！</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761210/extras/6e77283863560d74b4e580f42f6b248b.poster.avif?t=1770656584\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761210/extras/6e77283863560d74b4e580f42f6b248b.webm?t=1770656584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761210/extras/6e77283863560d74b4e580f42f6b248b.mp4?t=1770656584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>包括主角组灵梦、魔理沙在内，原作的少女们重装出战！<br>所有角色都会施展独特必杀技“符卡”！<br>运用各种各样的功放技能，称霸幻想乡吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >找到你最喜欢的势力！</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761210/extras/37dcdb5831b005355f3ba1b30037529d.poster.avif?t=1770656584\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761210/extras/37dcdb5831b005355f3ba1b30037529d.webm?t=1770656584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761210/extras/37dcdb5831b005355f3ba1b30037529d.mp4?t=1770656584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>博丽神社擅长内政和防卫、红魔馆在早期就能召唤强力兵种、<br>少女们归属的每个势力都有长处和短板！<br>寻找适合自己风格的势力，也是这个游戏的一大乐趣！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合理运用丰富多彩的兵种！</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761210/extras/887a9b22724ba46be40ec5c6ac3ab652.poster.avif?t=1770656584\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761210/extras/887a9b22724ba46be40ec5c6ac3ab652.webm?t=1770656584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761210/extras/887a9b22724ba46be40ec5c6ac3ab652.mp4?t=1770656584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>高速但是害怕长矛的骑兵、可以远程攻击但是害怕近战的弓兵、<br>擅长强力范围攻击的魔法使等等、游戏中存在多种多样的兵种。<br>针对不同势力和战局、选择合适的兵种！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >量大管饱的剧情模式！</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761210/extras/9b099284b0319956e46007c2d5b72783.poster.avif?t=1770656584\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761210/extras/9b099284b0319956e46007c2d5b72783.webm?t=1770656584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761210/extras/9b099284b0319956e46007c2d5b72783.mp4?t=1770656584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>一个人也能玩的剧情模式，包含20章以上的内容！<br>围绕着幻想乡的新异变，30多位少女你方唱罢我方登场！<br>引起这次风波的真凶到底是谁？幻想乡之谜等你来揭解开！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与全世界玩家对战的多人模式！</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761210/extras/7ca02a46e13aea42a4ef0563f586772b.poster.avif?t=1770656584\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761210/extras/7ca02a46e13aea42a4ef0563f586772b.webm?t=1770656584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761210/extras/7ca02a46e13aea42a4ef0563f586772b.mp4?t=1770656584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>本作支持最大六人的在线对战！<br>可以3v3，也可以大混战，游玩方式任君选择！<br>和同伴们组成队伍，挑战全世界的玩家吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >豪华作曲阵容，细致美术图像！</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761210/extras/dfec608c2907db396facbcae0632bc1f.poster.avif?t=1770656584\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761210/extras/dfec608c2907db396facbcae0632bc1f.webm?t=1770656584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761210/extras/dfec608c2907db396facbcae0632bc1f.mp4?t=1770656584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>圈内知名创作者担当编曲的背景音乐、精心设计完全原创的效果音、<br>令人耳目一新的主视觉图、还有细致入微的草原和水面等战场建模、<br>各个方面都超越了独立游戏的水平，为玩家献上开发者的匠心！",
